Package: NetworkChange
Title: Bayesian Package for Network Changepoint Analysis
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2026-01-22
Authors@R: c(person(given = c("Jong", "Hee"),
                    family = "Park",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
